race.comment: ATLANTIC RAIN (1) is a talented galloper who is unbeaten from two runs, the latest success coming over 1200m at Rockhampton. Hard to deny her credentials. THE KOBAY TRAIN (5) got off the mark with an impressive maiden win last time out over 1300m at Rockhampton. Nikki Olzard was in the saddle on that occasion and retains the mount. Capable of making it two on the trot. NEXT LEGACY (3) finished fifth over 1200m at Rockhampton when resuming last start, beaten only 0.8 lengths after being prominent at the bend. Strips fitter now so expect a better run this time. FABULEAN (2) finished second last time over 1100m at this track when resuming from a spell, beaten 0.6 lengths. The engagement of Sean Cormack is noteworthy. Meeting a deeper field this time but she is good enough to play a major role.
